    {
      "instruction": "<p>Whilst the fries are cooking, boil half a kettle</p><p>Peel and slice your <strong>shallot[s] </strong>finely</p><p>Peel and finely slice (don't chop!) your <strong>garlic</strong></p><p>Dissolve your <strong>chicken stock mix</strong>, <strong>tomato paste </strong>and <strong>gochujang paste </strong>(can't handle the heat? Go easy!) in 100ml <span class=\"text-purple\">[150ml] </span><span class=\"text-danger\">[175ml]</span> <strong>boiled water </strong>– this is your <strong>gochujang stock</strong></p>",
      "order": 2,
      "media": {
        "images": [
          {
            "image": "https://production-media.gousto.co.uk/cms/recipe-step-image/step-2-1690476954798-x200.jpg",
