    },
    {
      "instruction": "<p>Heat a large, wide-based pan (preferably non-stick) with a very generous drizzle of <strong>vegetable</strong> <strong>oil</strong> over a medium-high heat</p><p>Once hot, add the <strong>breaded</strong> <strong>chicken</strong> and cook for 5-6 min on each side or until golden and cooked through (no pink meat!) – this is your <strong>crispy chicken</strong></p>",
      "order": 5,
