        ]
      }
    },
    {
      "instruction": "<p>Once the fries are golden, remove the tray from the oven and push the fries to one side</p><p>Add the <strong>crispy</strong> <strong>chicken </strong>to the other side of the tray, then top with the <strong>gochujang sauce </strong>and<strong> grated cheese</strong></p><p>Return the tray to the oven for a further 4-5 min or until the cheese has melted – this is your <strong>Korean-style chicken parm</strong></p>",
